<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My First HTML Code</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f6ff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 60%;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">
    <h1>🚀 My First Code</h1>

    <p>Hello! My name is Habiba.</p>

    <p>This is my first HTML page created using GitHub Codespaces.</p>

    <p>I am learning how to code and this is the beginning of my journey into tech.</p>

    <button onclick="alert('Welcome to my first webpage!')">
        Click Me
    </button>
</div>

</body>
</html>